6cfc3410-d0b8-4674-bed1-1c01e3feff5a	57bb4a65-04b1-466e-90aa-f7bfc12c80b1	inbound	np@neilpatel.com	Neil Patel	richardson@superkabe.com	\N	How we drove 2,012% more visits through GEO	<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<style>.ck-link { text-decoration: underline; }</style>\r\n<style>@media only screen { .email * { word-break: break-word; } }\r\n@media screen and (max-width: 384px) { .mail-message-content { width: 414px !important; } }\r\n@media only screen and (max-width:600px) { .ck-mobile-font-size { font-size:50px !important; }  }</style>\r\n<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class="message-content" style="max-width:600px">\r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr><td>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">You probably already noticed a drop in your Google traffic.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">But just because one channel has dropped, it doesn’t mean your overall traffic can’t grow.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">For almost 2 years now, we’ve been optimizing for LLMs like ChatGPT and have the algorithm down.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Our approach increased RefiJet’s referral traffic by 2,012%. <a href="https://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4." target="_blank" class="ck-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" url-id="1849613811">Just check out the case study</a>.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">And we have countless other examples of doing the same for other companies in our “Work” section.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">If you want us to do the same for you…</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">​<a href="https://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4." target="_blank" class="ck-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" url-id="1849613812"><strong>Fill out this form to schedule a discovery call</strong></a>.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Cheers,</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Neil Patel</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">​</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em"><strong>P.S. </strong><em>Less than 6% of the marketers we talk to even know what GEO is. </em><a href="https://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4." target="_blank" class="ck-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" url-id="1849613812"><em>Get a head start before your competition does</em></a><em>.</em></p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">​<br>​</p>\r\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<small>\r\n<a href="https://e22d5796.unsubscribe.convertkit-mail4.com/gkuvm79npwt5hlw553nfrh8o7lwn2tmh29r3">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="https://preferences.convertkit-mail4.com/gkuvm79npwt5hlw553nfrh8o7lwn2tmh29r3">Update your profile</a> | 9710 River Trader St, Las Vegas, Nevada 89178\r\n<br>\r\n</small>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- -->\r\n<img src="https://e22d5796.open.convertkit-mail4.com/gkuvm79npwt5hlw553nfrh8o7lwn2tmh29r3" alt="">\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n	You probably already noticed a drop in your Google traffic.\r\n\r\nBut just because one channel has dropped, it doesn’t mean your\r\noverall traffic can’t grow.\r\n\r\nFor almost 2 years now, we’ve been optimizing for LLMs like\r\nChatGPT and have the algorithm down.\r\n\r\nOur approach increased RefiJet’s referral traffic by 2,012%. Just\r\ncheck out the case study (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4.\r\n).\r\n\r\nAnd we have countless other examples of doing the same for other\r\ncompanies in our “Work” section.\r\n\r\nIf you want us to do the same for you…\r\n\r\n​Fill out this form to schedule a discovery call (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4.\r\n).\r\n\r\nCheers,\r\n\r\nNeil Patel\r\n\r\n​\r\n\r\nP.S. Less than 6% of the marketers we talk to even know what GEO\r\nis. Get a head start before your competition does (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4.\r\n).\r\n\r\n​\r\n​\r\n\r\nUnsubscribe (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.unsubscribe.convertkit-mail4.com/gkuvm79npwt5hlw553nfrh8o7lwn2tmh29r3\r\