6143c81764938873924"><span style="text-decoration: inherit; display: inline-block; min-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;">Get started</span></a><!--[endif]----></div><!--[if gte mso 9]> </td></tr></table> <![endif]--><div data-editorblocktype="Text" style="background-color: transparent; margin: 10px;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><br></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="background-color: transparent; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">Hi Richardson,</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">Run pre-roll, mid-roll, and post-roll non-skippable ads to drive brand awareness across smart TVs and connected devices while they’re streaming media on networks such as HBO Max, Roku, Hulu, Food Network, CNN, Samsung TV Plus, LG, and more.</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Plus, we offer various targeting solutions for CTV campaigns. You can reach potential customers as they're watching specific content genres. You can go broad by targeting popular genres such as “Comedy” or “Action,” or you can reach your audience as they're watching their favorite sporting events, like “Football,” “Soccer,” or “Olympics.” This flexibility allows you to tailor your ads to the right audience and maximize your impact.</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Start using Connected TV today and begin serving your ads across high impact placements to generate large scale reach! Curious to learn more?<br></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; mso-line-height-rule: at-least; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #000; font-weight: normal; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Frutiger, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span></p></div><!--[if gte mso 9]> <table align="center"  style="border-collapse: collapse;border-spacin