e-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 1px; background-color: rgb(225, 211, 199);" height="0"><td>&nbsp;</td></tr> <![endif]--></tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--[if gte mso 9]> </th></tr></table><p style="height:0px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:0; padding:0;line-height: 0px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; background-color: transparent;"></p> <![endif]--><img src="https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/i/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAAA8AAAA" width="0" height="0" data-tracking /></body></html>	Microsoft Advertising enables you to engage in the moments that matter. |\r\n[View as a web page <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABAAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fpublic-usa.mkt.dynamics.com%252Fapi%252Fv1.0%252Forgs%252F1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843%252Fchannels%252Fmails%252Fvib%252F5a6ecfaf-3d82-a194-2c3f-35bfa09732f9_d41b2ad7-723d-f111-bec7-7ced8d3c7d63_6c260bfa-93e7-dc0d-439f-1bb1ceed081d_9f98eb0c-f1d4-f011-8543-7ced8d3b587b%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=KgvIAbKC%2Fjg2QgFa2gVGLcHbBeFW6lnwsiSbFMsF3Js%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf as a web page - US - T8>] [Microsoft Advertising header logo. <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABEAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fads.microsoft.com%252F%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=vLUHAw10kNKJbc4tPncxkj7APo00cArt8hvmj7zlWBs%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf Advertising home page>] [Banner] Reach your audience on smart TVs and connected devices [Get started <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABIAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fabout.ads.microsoft.com%252Fen-us%252Fh%252Fa%252Fmicrosoft-advertising%253Fs_cid%253Den-us-acq-other-src_ntr-sub_evergreen-flx_email8%2523%252C_msdynmkt_fn%253D%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%220%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=0H4Z9lBiaLRJUF5AQmGRaBeeKYlLBDRuHT5ycB3Hz7E%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf Get started - US - T8>] Hi Richardson, Run pre-roll, mid-roll, and post-roll non-skippable ads to drive brand awareness across smart TVs and connected devices while they’re streaming media on networks such as HBO Max, Roku, Hulu, Food Network, CNN, Samsung TV Plus, LG, and more. Plus, we offer various targeting solutions for CTV campaigns. You can reach potential customers as they're watching specific content genres. You can go broad by targeting popular genres such as “Comedy” or “Action,” or you can reach your audience as they're watching their favorite sporting events, like “Football,” “Soccer,” or “Olympics.” This flexibility allows you to tailor your ads to the right audience and maximize your impact. Start using Connected TV today and begin serving your ads across high impact placements to generate large scale reach! Curious to learn more? [Get started <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABMAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fabout.ads.microsoft.com%252Fen-us%252Fh%252Fa%252Fmicrosoft-advertising%253Fs_cid%253Den-us-acq-other-src_ntr-sub_evergreen-flx_email8%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=943qIbvNaUuX3m7idBCpDWsQN1dMPnWKzVg0Tpkw2Ls%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf started - US - T8>] Best, The Microsoft Advertising team\r\nWould you like some assistance getting started?\r\n[Connect with a Microsoft Advertising expert > <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABQAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fabout.ads.microsoft.com%252Fen%252Fget-started%252Fcontact-expert%252Funited-states%253Fs_cid%253Den-us-acq-other-src_ntr-sub_evergreen-flx_email8%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=k4VVTUa%2Flk%2BHZGqu6gvy2UiOIZmcuTnU%2FkpeEKm1jGc%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf with a Microsoft Advertising expert - T8>]\r\n†Offer details: Offer expires Tuesday, June 30, 2026 . Valid only for new Microsoft Advertising customers in the United States who are first party recipients of the offer email. A new Microsoft Advertising customer is one that has not had an active Microsoft Advertising account before. Limit one promotional offer per new Microsoft Advertising customer. To redeem this offer, customer must create a new Microsoft Advertising account with a primary payment method on file. Once customer completes Microsoft Advertising new customer account setup and spends at least $250 on advertising charges excluding taxes, the promotional credit of $500 will automatically be applied toward additional advertising spend thereafter, until credit is exhausted or the offer expires. For prepay accounts: the minimum qualifying ad spend amount is deducted directly from prepay funds. For postpay threshold accounts: the primary payment method is charged to collect the minimum qualifying ad spend once the account threshold is met. Customers are responsible for the payment of any taxes incurred. If you create your Microsoft Advertising account in a different currency than the one in which your promotional credit has been awarded, the actual amount of the promotional credit may be subject to foreign currency fluctuations. Any portion of the credit not used within ninety (90) days of credit award will expire and cannot be carried over or restored even if the Microsoft Advertising customer switches their payment method. If customer payment method fails, the promotional credit will not be applied. Microsoft Advertising will continue to run and accrue costs after any promotional credit has been exhausted. This offer may not be combined with any other offer, promotional code coupon or discount, separated, redeemed for cash, transferred, sold, or bartered. Microsoft, in its sole discretion, may close your account for any suspected abuse of this offer. Neither the original advertising qualifying spend nor the promotional credit are refundable, in whole or in part. See Microsoft Advertising Terms and Conditions for more details at sign-up. Other terms and conditions may apply. Microsoft reserves the right to cancel, change, or suspend this offer at any time without notice. Your offer may not cover spend accrued on campaigns run on Google Ads and Facebook Ads.\r\n[LinkedIn <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABUAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fshowcase%252Fmicrosoft-advertising%252F%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=7q8H5lEujNB9N%2FieKIpszxlhwfnprivnExCvKm110bo%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf>]\r\n[Instagram <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABYAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fwww.instagram.com%252Fmsftadvertising%252F%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=q2Uje3E7gj7cKuv4izSGbdqrfuAYyi0w7QXGk6Empb8%3D&msdynmkt_secretVersion=a3955a744d9049f88dd8bdc1907bf2bf>]\r\n[YouTube <https://public-usa.mkt.dynamics.com/api/orgs/1e56dbe2-1fcb-4e23-bd18-0898e86de843/r/XLznETTugE-d1FWUCYMAABcAAAA?msdynmkt_target=%7B%22TargetUrl%22%3A%22https%253A%252F%252Fwww.youtube.com%252Fchannel%252FUC1nblYoCAvQldqL_3Hn8uwg%22%2C%22RedirectOptions%22%3A%7B%225%22%3Anull%2C%221%22%3Anull%7D%7D&msdynmkt_digest=qEDygd4NFsDbZF