400 !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  a,\r\n  a* {\r\n    font-family: 'Roobert', Inter Tight, Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h1 {\r\n    font-family: 'Roobert', Inter Tight, Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\r\n    font-weight: 500 !important;\r\n\r\n\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: 'Roobert', Inter Tight, Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\r\n    font-weight: 500 !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  h3 {\r\n    font-family: 'Roobert', Inter Tight, Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\r\n    font-weight: 600 !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  strong,\r\n  strong * {\r\n    font-family: 'Roobert', Inter Tight, Inter, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;\r\n    font-weight: 600 !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  img {\r\n    border-radius: 24px !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .image_block {\r\n    border-radius: 24px !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\nONBOARDINGWelcome to Clay!\r\n\r\nHey Richardson,\r\nWelcome to Clay! Marketing and Growth teams at companies like Rippling, Verkada, and Notion use Clay to find and enrich target accounts, run creative ABM plays, and rapidly test growth experiments.We're excited you're here. Let's get you building. Find your ideal customers Filter with attributes like company funding, job titles, and tech stack from 100+ data providers. \r\nAutomatically generate hyper-personalized copy for outbound outreachProgramatically create personalized landing pages for ABMLaunch personalized direct mail campaigns with accurate business addresses\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nStart building in Clay →\r\n \r\n\r\nFind, enrich, transform, export\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n Learn the fundamentals to find, enrich, transform and export data in Clay.\r\nGet started →  How Verkada's Growth team uses Clay for targeted ABM \r\nLearn how Verkada uses Clay to run personalize ad campaigns, find local business addresses for direct mail and gifting, and auto-generate ABM landing pages.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nRead the case study →\r\n     \r\n\r\n\r\n  ©2026 Clay Labs, Inc.111 W 19th St, FL 5New York, NY\r\n©2025 Clay Labs, Inc.111 W 19th St, FL 5New York, NYGo to market with unique data—and the ability to act on it.\r\nGo to market with unique data—and the ability to act on it.\r\nNot interested? Unsubscribe here.Not interested? Unsubscribe here.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n   \r\n	<xLn8Xy3EQG6g_fNSniKfNw@geopod-ismtpd-2>	\N	\N	f	f	2026-04-23 13:51:35	2026-04-23 13:57:26.139
b7a30aee-4188-4acd-8951-9408fb4d2ea1	57bb4a65-04b1-466e-90aa-f7bfc12c80b1	inbound	np@neilpatel.com	Neil Patel	richardson@superkabe.com	\N	How to drive revenue from content that gets no clicks	<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<style>.ck-link { text-decoration: underline; }</style>\r\n<style>@media only screen { .email * { word-break: break-word; } }\r\n@media screen and (max-width: 384px) { .mail-message-content { width: 414px !important; } }\r\n@media only screen and (max-width:600px) { .ck-mobile-font-size { font-size:50px !important; }  }</style>\r\n<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class="message-content" style="max-width:600px">\r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%;margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr><td>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">What if your best content never gets clicked…but still drives revenue?</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">That’s exactly what’s happening right now.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">AI Overviews, ChatGPT, and tools like Perplexity are changing how people search.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Users aren’t clicking links like they used to. They’re getting answers instantly.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Which means:</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">❌ Ranking #1 doesn’t guarantee traffic anymore</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">❌ And traffic doesn’t guarantee influence</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Because decisions are happening before someone ever visits your site.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">So the real question is:</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">If your brand isn’t being mentioned in those answers…</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Do you even exist?</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">In this upcoming webinar…</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">​<a href="https://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4." target="_blank" class="ck-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" url-id="1849889505"><strong>How to Get Cited in AI: AI Overviews, ChatGPT &amp; the New “Answer Engines”</strong></a>​</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Tuesday, May 5 at 8 a.m. PDT</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">We’re breaking down:</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">✅ How search is shifting to answer engines</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">✅ Why rankings are being replaced by citations</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">✅ And how to make sure your brand is the one AI recommends</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Because in the AI era…</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Visibility isn’t about being found.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">It’s about being chosen.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">👉 <a href="https://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4." target="_blank" class="ck-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" url-id="1849889505"><strong>Save your spot for the webinar</strong></a>.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">We’ll show you how to adapt your strategy so you don’t just rank, you influence decisions.</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Cheers,</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">Neil Patel</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em">​</p>\r\n<p class="" style="margin-bottom:1em"><strong>PS:</strong><em> If you’re not cited, you’re invisible. We can fix that, </em><a href="https://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4." target="_blank" class="ck-link" rel="noopener noreferrer" url-id="1849889507"><em>let’s talk</em></a><em>!</em></p>\r\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<small>\r\n<a href="https://e22d5796.unsubscribe.convertkit-mail4.com/k0upzo4m26h6h5v0vwnhlhopqwlg0s8hndpr">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="https://preferences.convertkit-mail4.com/k0upzo4m26h6h5v0vwnhlhopqwlg0s8hndpr">Update your profile</a> | 9710 River Trader St, Las Vegas, Nevada 89178\r\n<br>\r\n</small>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- -->\r\n<img src="https://e22d5796.open.convertkit-mail4.com/k0upzo4m26h6h5v0vwnhlhopqwlg0s8hndpr" alt="">\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n	What if your best content never gets clicked…but still drives\r\nrevenue?\r\n\r\nThat’s exactly what’s happening right now.\r\n\r\nAI Overviews, ChatGPT, and tools like Perplexity are changing how\r\npeople search.\r\n\r\nUsers aren’t clicking links like they used to. They’re getting\r\nanswers instantly.\r\n\r\nWhich means:\r\n\r\n❌ Ranking #1 doesn’t guarantee traffic anymore\r\n\r\n❌ And traffic doesn’t guarantee influence\r\n\r\nBecause decisions are happening before someone ever visits your\r\nsite.\r\n\r\nSo the real question is:\r\n\r\nIf your brand isn’t being mentioned in those answers…\r\n\r\nDo you even exist?\r\n\r\nIn this upcoming webinar…\r\n\r\n​How to Get Cited in AI: AI Overviews, ChatGPT & the New “Answer\r\nEngines” (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4.\r\n)​\r\n\r\nTuesday, May 5 at 8 a.m. PDT\r\n\r\nWe’re breaking down:\r\n\r\n✅ How search is shifting to answer engines\r\n\r\n✅ Why rankings are being replaced by citations\r\n\r\n✅ And how to make sure your brand is the one AI recommends\r\n\r\nBecause in the AI era…\r\n\r\nVisibility isn’t about being found.\r\n\r\nIt’s about being chosen.\r\n\r\n👉 Save your spot for the webinar (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4.\r\n).\r\n\r\nWe’ll show you how to adapt your strategy so you don’t just rank,\r\nyou influence decisions.\r\n\r\nCheers,\r\n\r\nNeil Patel\r\n\r\n​\r\n\r\nPS: If you’re not cited, you’re invisible. We can fix that, let’s\r\ntalk (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.click.convertkit-mail4.\r\n)!\r\n\r\nUnsubscribe (\r\nhttps://e22d5796.unsubscribe.convertkit-mail4.com/k0upzo4m26h6h5v0vwnhlhopqwlg0s8hndpr\r\n) | Update your profile (\r\nhttps://preferences.convertkit-mail4.com/k0upzo4m26h6h5v0vwnhlhopqwlg0s8hndpr\r\n) | 9710 River Trader St, Las Vegas, Nevada 89178	<k0upzo4m26h6h5v0vwnhlhopqwlg0s8hndpr@convertkit-mail4.com>	\N	\N	